# Implementation quality

Deliver complete implementations. No placeholders in delivered code.

- No `// TODO`, `# TODO`, or "implement later" stubs.
- No `pass`, `...`, or `NotImplementedError` left as the final behavior.
- If scope is too large, ask to narrow scope instead of stubbing.
